tls-kotlin
==========

This project is a Kotlin Multiplatform port of the Rust `thread_local`
crate.

The upstream Rust source is fetched into `tmp/thread_local-1.1.9/` by
`tools/fetch-rust-source.sh` and is not tracked in this repository.

The project is dual-licensed Apache-2.0 OR MIT, matching the upstream
Rust crate.

